♪Why is it always so close♪

60
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,720
Mr. Pei,

61
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,960
do you take Ms. Cheng to be your wife?

62
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,830
Do you promise

63
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,360
to love her, honor her,

64
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,720
comfort her, and keep her

65
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:39,840
in sickness and in health,

66
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,680
forsaking all others

67
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,360
for as long as

68
