69
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,680
Yes, I do.

70
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,080
Likewise,

71
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,120
Ms. Cheng,

72
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:55,520
do you take Mr. Pei to be your husband?

73
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,440
Do you promise to love him, honor him,

74
00:03:57,730 --> 00:03:59,240
comfort him, and keep him

75
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:01,160
in sickness and in health,

76
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:03,000
forsaking all others for as long as

77
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,680
you both shall live?

78
00:04:06,290 --> 00:04:07,140
Yes, I do.

79
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:11,670
♪You always look at me secretly♪

80
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:18,570
♪Without saying anything♪

81
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:27,530
♪I always let you drink
the leftover milk♪

82
00:04:28,210 --> 00:04:32,420
♪Not sure if it's my fault♪

83
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:39,910
♪Feels like there's never enough time♪

84
00:04:42,350 --> 00:04:46,880
♪No one will hold an umbrella for me
when it rains anymore♪

85
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:53,840
♪I sit alone by the window,
watching the sunset♪

86
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:57,000
Let's pass on the love to others.

87
