Chen Xu!

92
00:05:21,170 --> 00:05:23,260
♪Beautiful youth♪

93
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:24,250
Great!

94
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:29,490
♪Share it with you♪

95
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,720
Will you be my girlfriend?

96
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,710
Say yes, say yes!

97
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,360
Hold her!

98
